# Installation errors
E8000 = The system has already been initialized.
E8001 = Username is required.
E8002 = Email address is required.
E8003 = Password is required.
E8004 = Domain is required.
E8005 = The domain is invalid. It must not contain spaces and must include at least one dot.
E8006 = The email address is invalid.
E8007 = That username is already taken.
E8008 = That email address is already registered.
E8009 = The key algorithm is not supported.
